sources.title: AMAZING CAST! About Alex (Full Movie) Drama, Millennial Big Chill | Aubrey Plaza, Max Greenfield
sources.description:
After the stress of adulthood takes its toll, seven college friends reunite.  Old crushes and rivalries are rekindled and a combination of wine, weed and an unexpected dog sends the weekend to unexpected places.

Directed by Jesse Zwick
2014
Starring 
Aubrey Plaza (White Lotus, Parks & Recreation)
Max Greenfield (New Girl, The Neighborhood)
Maggie Grace (Lost, Fear the Walking Dead)
Jane Levy (Suburgatory, Zoey's Extraordinary Playlist)
Jason Ritter (Raising Dion, Joan of Arcadia)
Nate Parker (The Great Debaters)
Max Minghella (The Handmaid's Tale, The Social Network)

Premiered at Tribeca Film Festival, 2014

#indiefilm #aubreyplaza #bigchill
